column2: End poverty in all its forms everywhere
column3: End hunger, achieve food security and improved nutrition and promote sustainable agriculture

column12: Make cities and human settlements inclusive, safe, resilient and sustainable

column17: Promote peaceful and inclusive societies for sustainable development, provide access to justice for all and build effective, accountable and inclusive institutions at all levels
column18: Strengthen the means of implementation and revitalize the Global Partnership for Sustainable Development
